snippet.title: Cloudy Super Mario Bros. U 2 - Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
The mod is out now! https://drive.google.com/drive/u/2/folders/12pAcqt93Jw2dAm2NU0Mkf5YjOaU6Ck2d

Cloudy Super Mario Bros. U 2 is a mod of NSMBU which will be releasing sooner than later.
My NSMBU Modding Discord Server: https://discord.gg/aZAaXVJ
Trailer 2: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qj4Z2FrRLds

* Note: Contrary to what is implied at the end of this trailer, the mod will be releasing in 2022

Check out ''FireFalls'' who made the amazing music for this trailer:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCejizOxEIxW77uf_KsM8-Cg

So why is this mod called Cloudy 2? Cloudy SMBU was my very first big solo nsmbu project, so I think it's fitting that my final big solo nsmbu project should be its sequel.

Cloudy SMBU2 will contain:
- 40+ brand new unique levels
- Over 100 new and revamped tilesets
- Retextures and remodels of NSMBU's original assets
- A brand new soundtrack with both original and remixed music
